com.plexobject.rx.scheduler

Interface Scheduler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Disposable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImmediateScheduler, NewThreadScheduler, ThreadPoolScheduler, TimerScheduler

    public interface Scheduler
extends Disposable
    This interface defines method to schedule callback function that is invoked upon each tick. It also defines a number of factory methods for creating different types of Schedulers.
